title: Concept Document_ Cymarion.pdf
summary: In-Fluid Acoustic Binary Signaling for Liquid-Filled Pipelines. Uses the pipeline’s fluid as a communication medium and avoids wiring or radio-based limitations. title: AI Isnt to Blame for the Rise in Layoffs
filename: AI Isnt to Blame for the Rise in Layoffs - Your Systems Are.docx
summary: AI is being blamed for layoffs, but the real issue is systemic incompetence in company operations. Poor role clarity and talent management are driving dysfunction. Without addressing these, AI will only automate existing problems — not solve them. Replacing humans with AI won’t fix dysfunction. It will just automate it, then amplify it.

title: Design Document_ Generic Execution Engine and Modeler.pdf
filename: Design Document_ Generic Execution Engine and Modeler.pdf
summary: Generic Execution Engine and Modeler provides a powerful, extensible platform for automating and orchestrating workflows across various domains. It uses a visual process modeler (e.g., BPMN) and a token-based execution engine. It offers the ability to: Model and visualize business processes or automated workflows in real-time. Track execution state through immutable tokens for auditability and historical analysis.

title: Course 17 Process CM v03.docx
summary: The 17th Course in Process CM is called Configuration Management Transforming Business Processes. The course focuses on Business Process Reengineering (BPR), Continuous Process Improvement (CPI), and Configuration Management (CM) The course lasts three days (24 hours total) and is designed to help you understand and analyze core business processes.

title: Echo Companion backend.pdf
summary: Local-first user interaction system ensures privacy and control over data. Only meta-data and necessary updates are sent to the central server (Firebase) when the user triggers a rebuild. Pull-to-Rebuild functionality allows the user to trigger the rebuild process manually when they want to update their world.
